Package com.esri.mo2.cs.gdb

Contains classes that implement access to the geodetic database.

          Description

Interface Summary
CoordinateSystemSetTable Represents a set of coordinate systems, for example, all the coordinate systems in US State Plane 1983.
GeodeticTable Represents a geodetic table within the geodetic database
Parameter A Parameter represents a parametric value which can be converted using a linear and/or an angular unit

DoubleParameter Represents a unit-less double parameter

GeodeticDatabaseEntry represents an entry within the database.

GeodeticPropertyFile represents access to the underlying property file containing the Geodetic Database

Exception Summary
InvalidRowDataException this is the generic row exception thrown by com.esri.mo2.cs.gdb package methods
 

Package com.esri.mo2.cs.gdb Description

Contains classes that implement access to the geodetic database. The geodetic database contains all standard geodetic object data, thus separating software from data.
